data.description: Come see this ranch-style home with 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths, offering 1421 sq ft of comfortable living space. Situated on a spacious .60 acre parcel, this property provides ample room for outdoor enjoyment.  A detached 3-car garage with 2 being on solid concrete and third is attached but bare floor.  Perfect for storing vehicles and equipment.  While you may notice the need for some cosmetic enhancements, it offers a fantastic opportunity to personalize and add value to your investment.  Here waiting for you to make it your own!   HVAC new in 2023. Water heater and sump pump 2018.
